subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Kyle Busch turned a lap at 169.485 miles an hour to win the pole for the Nascar Sprint Cup race Sunday at Pocono Raceway.
snippet: Kyle Busch turned a lap at 169.485 miles an hour to win the pole for the Nascar Sprint Cup race Sunday at Pocono Raceway.
